<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL6">
<l>maṟañcuvar matiḷe ṭuttu maṟumaikkē veṟumai pūṇṭu</l>
<l>puṟañcuva rōṭṭai māṭam puraḷumpō taṟiya māṭṭīr</l>
<l>aṟañcuva rāki niṉṟa varaṅkaṉārk kāṭcey yātē</l>
<l>puṟañcuvar kōlañ ceytu puṭkavvak kiṭakkiṉ ṟīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Raising a fortification made of a wall of evil,</l>
<l>And adopting poverty with respect to the next world,</l>
<l>You do not know the time when the mansion with holes</l>
<l>—a [mere] outer wall—</l>
<l>will tumble over.</l>
<l>Beautifying the outer wall</l>
<l>and not serving the great [Lord] of Raṅgam, the wall of dharma,</l>
<l>you lie for the birds to snatch [your body]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
